summary: An Ordinance accepting a quit-claim deed from Rolland H. Denny and Alice K. Denny, his wife, to the City of Seattle, dated the 29th day of July, A. D. 1907, to certain property in the Replat of John J. McGilvra's Addition to the City of Seattle, and the south half of Block 19 of John J. McGilvar's Second Addition to the City of Seattle.
